(239, 'dororo', 'Dororo', 'Dororo', 23, 'https://animesprout.com/kitsuImages/cover_41083.jpg', 'Supernatural, Action, Adventure', 'In Japan&#39;s Warring States period, Lord Daigo Kagemitsu makes a pact with 12 demons, exchanging his unborn son for the prosperity of his lands. The child is born malformed and is set adrift in a river, while Kagemitsu&#39;s lands thrive as promised. Years later, young thief Dororo encounters the mysterious &#34;Hyakkimaru&#34;, a boy whose arms are blades and whose visionless eyes seem able to see monsters.', 'subbed', 'MAPPA', 'Finished', 'R-Violence, Profanity', 'https://animesprout.com/kitsuImages/banner_41083.png', 'Jan 07, 2019', 0),
